{"title_page": "Underdog (Alicia Keys song)", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Underdog\n| cover      = Alicia Keys - Underdog.png\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Alicia Keys]]\n| album      = [[Alicia (album)|Alicia]]\n| released   = {{Start date|2020|01|09}}\n| format     =\n* [[Music download|Digital download]]\n* [[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| recorded   = 2019\n| studio     =\n| length     = {{duration|m=3|s=28}}\n| genre      = <!-- Please source genres -->\n| label      = [[RCA Records|RCA]]\n| writer     =\n* [[Alicia Keys]]\n* [[Johnny McDaid]]\n* [[Ed Sheeran]]\n* [[Amy Wadge]]\n* [[Jonny Coffer]]\n* [[Foy Vance]]\n| producer   =\n* Alicia Keys\n* Johnny McDaid\n| prev_title = [[The Christmas Song]]\n| prev_year  = 2019\n| next_title = \n| next_year  = \n| misc       = {{External music video|1={{YouTube|izyZLKIWGiA|\"Underdog\"}}}}\n}}\n\n\"'''Underdog'''\" is a song by American singer and songwriter [[Alicia Keys]]. It was written by Keys, [[Johnny McDaid]], [[Ed Sheeran]], [[Amy Wadge]], [[Jonny Coffer]] and [[Foy Vance]], and produced by Keys and McDaid. The song was released as the second  single from Keys' seventh studio album ''[[Alicia (album)|Alicia]]'' (2020).\n\nOn 27 March 2020, the song was remixed by Keys and featured [[reggae]] singers [[Protoje]] and [[Chronixx]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dancehallmag.com/2020/03/27/music/alicia-keys-recruits-chronixx-protoje-for-underdog-remix-listen.html|title=Alicia Keys Recruits Chronixx & Protoje For 'Underdog (Remix)': Listen|work=DancehallMag|last=Collins|first=Latoya|date=March 27, 2020|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Music video==\nThe music video was released on January 9, 2020.<ref>https://mtv.com/news/3152173/alicia-keys-underdog-music-video/</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br/>position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[ARIA Digital Track 