ys and featured [[reggae]] singers [[Protoje]] and [[Chronixx]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dancehallmag.com/2020/03/27/music/alicia-keys-recruits-chronixx-protoje-for-underdog-remix-listen.html|title=Alicia Keys Recruits Chronixx & Protoje For 'Underdog (Remix)': Listen|work=DancehallMag|last=Collins|first=Latoya|date=March 27, 2020|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Music video==\nThe music video was released on January 9, 2020.<ref>https://mtv.com/news/3152173/alicia-keys-underdog-music-video/</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br/>position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[ARIA Digital Track Chart|Australia Digital Tracks]] ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cdn.aria.com.au/pdfs/1FAF5F78CAC02455E60C0DB8970BCE15B325448ADF880DA5DF9FD10A8B3FF9B8/ARIA%20Digital%20Tracks%20Chart.pdf?seq=30|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 40 Digital Tracks|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=February 10, 2020|accessdate=February 8, 2020}}</ref>\n| 36\n|-\n{{single chart|Flanders|13|artist=Alicia Keys|song=Underdog|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 7, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Wallonia|11|artist=Alicia Keys|song=Underdog|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 14, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Czech Republic|71|year=2020|week=10|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 9, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Germany2|37|songid=1937007|artist=Alicia Keys|song=Underdog|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 27, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Mexico Ingles Airplay]] (''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'')<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/mexico-ingles/2020-02-22 | work = [[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]| title = Mexico Ingles Airplay}}</ref>\n| 22\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch40|18|year=2020|week=13|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 28, 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch100|54|artist=Alicia Keys|song=Underdog|rowheader=true|accessdate=March 21, 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=